content_text: When I wake up, when I opened my eyes in the morning, the first thing which I do is pray. I wash my teeth and then I had to office. With my bike and I start working. It's a great feeling because I get to meet a lot of people every day doing the same thing in different ways, learning new aspects of doing the same thing and then giving feedback to the advisor as I am equality evaluated.
